= A generic type for classes that receive collection objects as results =

The CollectionOperationListener type allows a class to declare that it is able to
receive a Collection object as a result of an operation.

= to_event_receiver =

Wrap this event listener object to a standard EventReceiver object. Any Collection
objects will then be treated appropriately, and passed to the original object.

= on_collection =

Called when an operation has a Collection to submit.
